data.description: Gorgeous 4 side brick one-story home in Bridgewood Ranch.  As you step into this lovely 3 bed, 2 bath house, you'll be greeted by the warmth and comfort of a well-designed open floor plan with additional flex space that can be used as formal dining, office or play area. You will fall in love with the bright kitchen featuring  kitchen island, stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash, large oversized SS sink and breakfast area. New roof recently installed. Generous size owner's suite and master bath that includes separate shower and garden tub. REFRIGERATOR INCLUDED!!! Seller WILL CONTRIBUTE $5K towards buyers closing cost. Situated near shopping, dining, and entertainment options, you'll have easy access to everything you need for a comfortable lifestyle. Conveniently located in acclaimed award winning ISD. Come see it today!
